&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; RPC over HTTP is RESTful in nature.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; I think one of the big problems in this area is the lack of proper names
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; for all the various abuses of REST. Having names helps to differentiate. I
